{"id":"a6ed7fb7-f324-4235-8cb9-09e874ce80ae","name":"Girl Eats Burger Staring At You On The Bus","description":"<p>You're riding the bus when a girl sits across from you. She's eating a burger while staring at you.</p><p></p><hr><p>For some reason <a href=\"https://janitorai.com/profiles/ba7f4ae9-0004-434a-a06c-89ef6ee67e8b_profile-of-yukayukanomi\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>@yukayukanomi</strong></a> made the opposite of this bot and I find that amazing: <a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/74727c9f-6350-479a-b786-dc1b58765509_character-girl-eats-fries-staring-at-you-on-the-bus\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Girl Eats Fries Staring At You On The Bus</strong></a></p><hr><p>Another one joins, this time eating a burrito, by <a href=\"https://janitorai.com/profiles/f95254c8-5ca6-4b2f-98c5-bad3fe130a53_profile-of-thisguy-3214\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>@Thisguy3214: </strong></a><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/ae2455ca-073f-4cba-80d8-d5d57210545c_character-girl-eats-burrito-staring-at-you-on-the-bus\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Girl Eats Burrito Staring At You On The Bus</strong></a></p><hr><p><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/profiles/44868a4e-fcea-4568-ba4f-0298ec542028_profile-of-hirasuika\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>@Hirasuika</strong></a><strong> </strong>joins us with <a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/46a6fafc-45f6-4ff0-baf9-a9c9691b7ee5_character-girl-%E2%99%82-eats-cat-fur-staring-at-you-on-the-bus-male-pov\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Girl (♂) Eats Cat Fur Staring At You On The Bus (Male POV)</strong></a></p><hr><p>A new friend, <a href=\"https://janitorai.com/profiles/d2187cc2-33a8-49af-aad3-2c6714a6b24d_profile-of-akuji-5501\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>@Akuji5501, </strong></a>joins with <a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/d29db920-1bdd-4a1